extendedInfo.description: [f]Technology create this application due to help indonesiangoverment to promote Indonesian culture to International people and hope more people will know the Indonesian as one of the culture richest country.Acer Iconia Hack Day is one of indonesian android appcompetition, in this competition developer ahould create 1application that could run smoothly in acer iconia in 24HR.Hallet has become the best 9 out of 400 contestants.                                                      Regards from [f]Technology, we are very happy to haveyour feedback.
